{"tid":1553760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【賽後檢討】hit or run？","createTime":"2019-09-08T16:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T05:11:27.000Z","uid":37897,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"601aac7cb5a3ca769dfe214cf659e6a6926890e9","tid":1553760,"uid":37897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:55:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以後同我轉曬throw and run 唔該！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n事實係大家武力上既不對等，陣地對峙根本就無得打，相信呢點係無可否認。<br />\n<br />\n既然係咁，全撚部同我轉曬做遠攻唔該。<br />\n<br />\n1.易棄易攜<br />\n<br />\n2.無痕跡留低<br />\n<br />\n3.無需帶gear，black boc上陣throw and  run<br />\n<br />\n4.最重要係唔驚俾人逗到有豬咀 or 其他攻擊性武器（e.g行山仗）<br />\n<br />\n其實大家都錫身呢樣真係無可否認，亦唔需要認，因為無必要受傷<br />\n<br />\n大家問心，所有拎鐵通，行山仗既，有幾多個有打過狗一下咁多？<br />\n<br />\n做法唔完善，有進步空間，AI示威！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">願榮光歸於香港！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e7fcec33e0740238624956ad80bfe8f76e71c8b2","tid":1553760,"uid":52043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:56:16.000Z","msg":"「緊急」十八區中學人鏈聽朝要人 入嚟睇下有冇你舊校<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1553681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1553681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1c57bb5632e399a50dd17ab334c79d3616564e8c","tid":1553760,"uid":37897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:56:55.000Z","msg":"幫手推唔該，不受傷，不被捕呀"},{"pid":"2525df350950050c400a121373a1fa4d39085f50","tid":1553760,"uid":37897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:58:32.000Z","msg":"賽後檢討！！！"},{"pid":"95ee13b640aaafe0f5a71dada2b963232547a044","tid":1553760,"uid":37897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:00:06.000Z","msg":"認真post無人理"},{"pid":"5dc63a7f79ac5ad77510a49a427a302e21f04111","tid":1553760,"uid":37897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:01:49.000Z","msg":"又要自推"},{"pid":"cf3020ce5f52268bc12390155bc366161